trans-unit.source: Adds dispatcher synchronization behavior to a dispatcher configuration element so that a WCF service program can send message replies to client applications asynchronously.
trans-unit.target: Lägger till dispatcher synkroniseringsbeteende en dispatcher konfigurationselementet så att ett program för WCF-tjänsten kan skicka meddelandesvar på klientprogram asynkront.

trans-unit.source: Creates a new instance of the <xref href="System.ServiceModel.Configuration.DispatcherSynchronizationElement"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Skapar en ny instans av den <xref href="System.ServiceModel.Configuration.DispatcherSynchronizationElement"> </xref> klass.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets whether asynchronous message sending is enabled.
trans-unit.target: Hämtar eller anger om möjligheten att skicka asynkront meddelande är aktiverad.

trans-unit.source: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> if asynchronous send is enabled; otherwise, <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>om asynkron sändning aktiveras; Annars <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: Gets the type of the <xref href="System.ServiceModel.Configuration.DispatcherSynchronizationElement"></xref> behavior extension.

Copies a sub-element that defines dispatcher behavior extensions from the specified configuration <xref href="System.ServiceModel.Configuration.ServiceModelExtensionElement"></xref> into the current <xref href="System.ServiceModel.Configuration.DispatcherSynchronizationElement"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Kopierar ett underelement som definierar dispatcher beteende tilläggen från den angivna konfigurationen <xref href="System.ServiceModel.Configuration.ServiceModelExtensionElement"> </xref> till aktuellt <xref href="System.ServiceModel.Configuration.DispatcherSynchronizationElement"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.ServiceModel.Configuration.ServiceModelExtensionElement"></xref> object that provides synchronization sub-elements.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.ServiceModel.Configuration.ServiceModelExtensionElement"> </xref> objekt som innehåller underordnade element för synkronisering.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the maximum number of received messages that can be buffered by the dispatcher.
trans-unit.target: Hämtar eller anger det maximala antalet mottagna meddelanden som kan buffras av dispatcher.

trans-unit.source: A number that represents a quantity of messages.
trans-unit.target: Ett tal som representerar en mängd av meddelanden.
